{"title":"南沙的风","authors":["孙红林"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":3,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"南沙的风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孙红林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风，从南边吹来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带着海的气息，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"升腾起隐隐的硝烟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有，男子汉特有的韵味。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或许，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹拂过顽强的礁石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或许，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲吻过战士的身躯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或许，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凝结着一片片期待。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它诉说无数的故事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它蕴藉真切的情肠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它把默默的奉献"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送给四面八方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"*作者是南沙永署礁守礁战士"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}